com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.extension
Interface IDecoratorSemanticService

public interface IDecoratorSemanticService

Provides a management layer for com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.topology/decoratorSemantic extensions.

This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.

Since:
1.0
